snippet.title: Oddmar - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Follow Oddmar on his adventure through the mythical world of Vikings. Explore vibrantly crafted Nordic lands in this action-adventure platformer.

Coming 19th April 2018. You can pre-order now!
https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/oddmar/id1247397901?ls=1&mt=8

Join Oddmar’s community at
http://facebook.com/oddmargame
http://twitter.com/oddmargame
